data.description: Single story home and attached casita with its own entrance for all your guests, relatives, or your business. Oversized 3-car finished garage and exterior RV pad. Open floor plan with LVP flooring and carpeted bedrooms, lots of storage, and wood-burning stove in the living room. Master bedroom with slider access to the backyard and large walk-in closet that connects directly to the laundry room. Welcome home to Santa Maria Ranch. Home is easy to view, call me today.......... Attached oversized 3-car garage and exterior RV pad with nearby water spigot installed for easy fill-up. This home has ample space to store all your toys can be used on the 100’s of miles of trails in the Northern Nevada area or up in beautiful Lake Tahoe. Features close proximity to schools and shopping and only minutes to Carson City and Lake Tahoe, and a short drive to Reno and the Reno Tahoe Industrial Complex via USA Parkway. Inspired by a Nevada lifestyle, located in the extremely sought-after Santa Maria Ranch, nestled at the beginning of Dayton Valley, Santa Maria has a beautiful community park with a soccer field, basketball court, tot play area, picnic tables, and BBQ areas. There is a regional park as well with miles of river front walking trails, picnic areas, a fishing pier, raft launch point, exercise stations, all through the original old growth trees along the Carson River.
